Global Miso Paste Market Insights
Miso Paste Market size was valued at USD 1.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.3 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Miso Paste Market Overview
The global miso paste market is valued at approximately USD 5.3 billion in 2024 and is projected to grow at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 4.3% from 2024 to 2031. The growing consumer demand for plant-based, protein-rich, and fermented food products is a primary factor driving the market's expansion. Moreover, the increasing popularity of Japanese cuisine worldwide and the rising awareness regarding the health benefits of fermented foods are expected to further fuel the market. Asia-Pacific holds the largest share of the market due to high consumption levels in Japan, South Korea, and China, while North America and Europe are emerging as key growth regions, driven by rising demand for ethnic and healthy food products.

